OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781486246
OL,3,C'Giant of the Labour movement' Roy
OL,4,CHattersley dies
OL,6,FRoy Hattersley, the former Labour
OL,7,Fdeputy leader, has died aged 93, with
OL,8,FSir Keir Starmer leading tributes to
OL,9,Fhis "decades of service".
OL,11,FKnown as Labour's "nearly man," he
OL,12,Ffailed to gain the leadership of the
OL,13,Fparty he loved and spent more than two
OL,14,Fdecades of his 33 years as an MP on
OL,15,Fthe opposition benches.
OL,17,FPrime Minister Sir Keir wrote on X:
OL,18,F"Roy Hattersley was a giant of the
OL,19,FLabour movement.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@XO]sD@SOUsD@_O]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
