FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781486246
OL,3,C'Giant of the Labour movement' Roy
OL,4,CHattersley dies
OL,6,FAfter standing down from the House of
OL,7,FCommons in 1997, he was elevated to
OL,8,Fthe House of Lords as Baron Hattersley
OL,9,Fof Sparkbrook.
OL,11,FAlongside his political career, he was
OL,12,Fa prolific author, publishing more
OL,13,Fthan 20 books including biographies,
OL,14,Fhistories and memoirs.
OL,16,FHis wife Maggie Pearlstine survives
OL,17,Fhim.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
